headline: Simon速 Acquires Remaining Interest in Taubman Realty Group
summary: Simon速, a real estate investment trust engaged in the ownership of premier shopping, dining, entertainment and mixed-use destinations, today announced that it has closed on the acquisition of the remaining 12% interest in The Taubman Realty Group Limited Partnership ("TRG") which it did not own in exchange for 5.06 million limited partnership units in Simon Property Group L.P.
